      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIGHTY HEIGHTY (2) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Paw Kattia (26.52) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Likely to feature again. BARKING BLUE (8) ran a good time (26.27) when placing three back at this track but has missed the frame since, last time out finishing sixth (17.03) at Healesville. Well placed here and should do much better. PAY THE REG (4) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from six starts. Hit the frame latest (23.42) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Suited here and expected to run well. PEPPER PIE (1) has won at this course and distance so worth including.",
